Description:
Linux_LANEndpoint class provider implementation. The following CMPI instance methods are supported:
  • Cleanup
  • EnumerateInstanceNames
  • EnumerateInstances
  • GetInstance
  • MethodCleanup
  • InvokeMethod

Interface Type : Common Manageability Programming Interface ( CMPI )
